OL,3,GOrkney & Shetland
OL,4,
OL,5,CToday:FShetland will have a dry day
OL,6,Fwith some high cloud and bright or
OL,7,Fsunny spells. Dry with some early
OL,8,Fbrightness across Orkney but outbreaks
OL,9,Fof rain spreading east in the
OL,10,Fafternoon.
OL,11,
OL,12,CTonight:FCloud and outbreaks of rain
OL,13,Fand drizzle across Orkney this evening
OL,14,Fgradually extending across Shetland
OL,15,Fduring the early hours. Becoming misty
OL,16,Fwith fog patches. Light winds.
OL,17,
OL,18,CWednesday:FMisty start with some
OL,19,Fdrizzly rain. Otherwise a cloudy day
OL,20,Fwith occasional light rain, but some
OL,21,Fdrier weather too.
OL,23,QppppppppppppppppppppGSource: Met Office
OL,24,ANext Page  BWeather  CReg News  FReg TV
