OL,3,GOrkney & Shetland
OL,4,
OL,5,COutlook for Thursday to Saturday:FDry
OL,6,Falthough rather cloudy on Thursday.
OL,7,FMainly dry with some sunshine on
OL,8,FFriday, perhaps a shower across
OL,9,FShetland later. Chance of a light
OL,10,Fshower on Saturday otherwise dry.
OL,23,QppppppppppppppppppppGSource: Met Office
